ESET NOD32 Smart Security- A new version of the complex antivirus NOD32 with cloud technology ESET Live Grid. Solution "all-in-one" with multi-level protection. Protect your computer or laptop from loss or theft with the functionality of the new Anti-Theft component. The Anti-Theft feature allows you to locate and recover a lost or stolen laptop or computer. 
After you mark on the ESET Anti-Theft web portal that the computer is lost or stolen, the device is automatically monitored and allows you to monitor the position of the laptop or computer on the map using Wi-Fi. When a lost or stolen device connects to the network, you have access to all the information gathered on the Anti-Theft portal. 

Antivirus NOD32- A new anti-virus solution from ESET, offering improved heuristic analysis of unknown threats, ESET's "cloud" technology for determining the reputation of files and an updated interface. It includes the ability to automatically scan a computer during its idle time, scan files directly at boot time, and the ability to undo installed updates.
